s=title> The story of Loki Xi (please crit) Part 1 done.</span><hr size=1> er, here's a quick outline of the first part of the story.<br>
<br>
TITLE:<br>
<br>
Main character(s):<br>
        1. Loki Xi, age 16<br>
        2. Danniel Xi, age 21<br>
Secondary characters:<br>
        1. Zak Tsaroth (Loki's best friend)<br>
        2. Gerald Mandor (Loki's rival)<br>
        3. <br>
        4.<br>
        5.<br>
<br>
Setting: Neo Tokyo, slums<br>
Time: Semi-Futuristic, The year is 2057<br>
Global events: WW3 just ended<br>
Date: May 21, 2021<br>
<br>
Plot: Loki and his sister Danniel (she prefers Dannie) live in the slums of Neo-Tokyo. One day Danie discovers an odd doorway that was never noticed before. Her curiosity aroused she tried to open the door. She couldn't so she asked her broher to break the door in. He did so and they had accidentaly stumbled upon a secret gov't facility. They barley make it out of there alive. Now they need to get off planet into the wilds of space where there is little or no law at all. Hopefully they can escape the gov't and find a home elsewere. They spend a week getting a transport off planet all the while dodging the agents of that gov't facility (they still have no clue as to what gov't they were part of.) The agents believed they had seen top secret plans. But what had really happend was that dannie walked into an odd room and the door closed behind her. The room was for a nural uplink officer and danni couldn't get out of the room. The nural transmiters started sending data overloading dannies brain. Now she can comunicate with any machine that can recieve remote connections, sometimes being able to control them. Un fourtuanatly she has become weak and relies on her brother alot.<br>
<br>
